{"1":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1.15","c":"حمٓ","d":"ha-meem","e":"Ha Meem","i":"حٰمٓۚ"}],"a":{"g":"Ha, Meem."}},"2":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.6","c":"تَنزِيلُ","d":"tanzīlu","e":"(The) revelation","i":"تَنۡزِيۡلُ"},{"b":"1.8","h":"2.63","c":"ٱلۡكِتَٰبِ","d":"l-kitābi","e":"(of) the Book","i":"الۡكِتٰبِ"},{"b":"2.8","h":"4.4","c":"مِنَ","d":"mina","e":"(is) from","i":"مِنَ"},{"b":"3.1","h":"5.03","c":"ٱللَّهِ","d":"l-lahi","e":"Allah","i":"اللّٰهِ"},{"b":"3.9","h":"6.69","c":"ٱلۡعَزِيزِ","d":"l-ʿazīzi","e":"the All-Mighty","i":"الۡعَزِيۡزِ"},{"b":"4.9","h":"8.55","c":"ٱلۡحَكِيمِ","d":"l-ḥakīmi","e":"the All-Wise","i":"الۡحَكِيۡمِ"}],"a":{"g":"The revelation of the Book is from Allah, the Exalted in Might, the Wise."}},"3":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.6","c":"إِنَّ","d":"inna","e":"Indeed","i":"اِنَّ"},{"b":"1.1","h":"1.9","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"in","i":"فِى"},{"b":"1.3","h":"2.29","c":"ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ","d":"l-samāwāti","e":"the heavens","i":"السَّمٰوٰتِ"},{"b":"2.7","h":"4.98","c":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ","d":"wal-arḍi","e":"and the earth","i":"وَالۡاَرۡضِ"},{"b":"3.7","h":"6.84","c":"لَأٓيَٰتٖ","d":"laāyātin","e":"surely (are) Signs","i":"لَاٰيٰتٍ"},{"b":"4.9","h":"9.14","c":"لِّلۡمُؤۡمِنِينَ","d":"lil'mu'minīna","e":"for the believers","i":"لِّلۡمُؤۡمِنِيۡنَؕ"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, within the heavens and earth are signs for the believers."}},"4":{"w":[{"b":"0.05","h":"0.75","c":"وَفِي","d":"wafī","e":"And in","i":"وَفِىۡ"},{"b":"0.53","h":"1.61","c":"خَلۡقِكُمۡ","d":"khalqikum","e":"your creation","i":"خَلۡقِكُمۡ"},{"b":"1.5","h":"3.42","c":"وَمَا","d":"wamā","e":"and what","i":"وَمَا"},{"b":"2.0","h":"4.54","c":"يَبُثُّ","d":"yabuthu","e":"He disperses","i":"يَبُثُّ"},{"b":"2.9","h":"6.08","c":"مِن","d":"min","e":"of","i":"مِنۡ"},{"b":"3.9","h":"7.16","c":"دَآبَّةٍ","d":"dābbatin","e":"(the) moving creatures","i":"دَآبَّةٍ"},{"b":"7.8","h":"11.76","c":"ءَايَٰتٞ","d":"āyātun","e":"(are) Signs","i":"اٰيٰتٌ"},{"b":"8.8","h":"13.84","c":"لِّقَوۡمٖ","d":"liqawmin","e":"for a people","i":"