","h":"0.4","c":"وَبَدَا","d":"wabadā","e":"And (will) appear","i":"وَبَدَا"},{"b":"0.93","h":"1.72","c":"لَهُمۡ","d":"lahum","e":"to them","i":"لَهُمۡ"},{"b":"1.4","h":"2.75","c":"سَيِّـَٔاتُ","d":"sayyiātu","e":"(the) evil","i":"سَيِّاٰتُ"},{"b":"2.7","h":"5.07","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"(of) what","i":"مَا"},{"b":"3.0","h":"5.88","c":"عَمِلُواْ","d":"ʿamilū","e":"they did","i":"عَمِلُوۡا"},{"b":"4","h":"7.45","c":"وَحَاقَ","d":"waḥāqa","e":"and (will) envelop","i":"وَحَاقَ"},{"b":"4.8","h":"8.89","c":"بِهِم","d":"bihim","e":"them","i":"بِهِمۡ"},{"b":"6.1","h":"10.42","c":"مَّا","d":"mā","e":"what","i":"مَّا"},{"b":"6.4","h":"11.04","c":"كَانُواْ","d":"kānū","e":"they used","i":"كَانُوۡا"},{"b":"7.3","h":"12.62","c":"بِهِۦ","d":"bihi","e":"[at it]","i":"بِهٖ"},{"b":"7.9","h":"13.8","c":"يَسۡتَهۡزِءُونَ","d":"yastahziūna","e":"(to) mock","i":"يَسۡتَهۡزِءُوۡنَ"}],"a":{"g":"And the evil consequences of what they did will appear to them, and they will be enveloped by what they used to ridicule."}},"34":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.38","c":"وَقِيلَ","d":"waqīla","e":"And it will be said","i":"وَقِيۡلَ"},{"b":"0.83","h":"1.6","c":"ٱلۡيَوۡمَ","d":"l-yawma","e":"Today","i":"الۡيَوۡمَ"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.19","c":"نَنسَىٰكُمۡ","d":"nansākum","e":"We forget you","i":"نَنۡسٰٮكُمۡ"},{"b":"3.5","h":"5.82","c":"كَمَا","d":"kamā","e":"as","i":"كَمَا"},{"b":"4.2","h":"7.02","c":"نَسِيتُمۡ","d":"nasītum","e":"you forgot","i":"نَسِيۡتُمۡ"},{"b":"5.2","h":"8.86","c":"لِقَآءَ","d":"liqāa","e":"(the) meeting","i":"لِقَآءَ"},{"b":"7.3","h":"11.33","c":"يَوۡمِكُمۡ","d":"yawmikum","e":"(of) this Day of yours","i":"يَوۡمِكُمۡ"},{"b":"8.3","h":"13.2","c":"هَٰذَا","d":"hādhā","e":"(of) this Day of yours","i":"هٰذَا"},{"b":"9.2","h":"14.92","c":"وَمَأۡوَىٰكُمُ","d":"wamawākumu","e":"and your abode","i":"وَمَاۡوٰٮكُمُ"},{"b":"10.6","h":"17.52","c":"ٱلنَّارُ","d":"l-nāru","e":"(is) the Fire","i":"النَّارُ"},{"b":"17.2","h":"19.62","c":"وَمَا","d":"wamā","e":"and not","i":"وَمَا"},{"b":"17.9","h":"20.75","c":"لَكُم","d":"lakum","e":"for you","i":"لَـكُمۡ"},{"b":"19.","h":"22.38","c":"مِّن","d":"min","e":"any","i":"مِّنۡ"},{"b":"19.5","h":"22.39","c":"نَّـٰصِرِينَ","d":"nāṣirīna","e":"helpers","i":"نّٰصِرِيۡنَ"}],"a":{"g":"And it will be said, \"Today We will forget you as you forgot the meeting of this Day of yours, and your refuge is the Fire, and for you there are no helpers."}},"35":{"w":[{"b":"0.12","h":"0.55","c":"ذَٰلِكُم","d":"dhālikum","e":"That","i":"ذٰلِكُمۡ"},{"b":"1.9","h":"2.65","c":"بِأَنَّكُمُ","d":"bi-annakumu","e":"(is) because you","i":"بِاَنَّكُمُ"},{"b":"4.0","h":"5.18","c":"ٱتَّخَذۡتُمۡ","d":"ittakhadhtum","e":"took","i":"اتَّخَذۡتُمۡ"},{"b":"5.0","h":"7.42","c":"ءَايَٰتِ","d":"āyāti","e":"(the) Verses","i":"اٰيٰتِ"},{"b":"6.1","h":"9.48","c":"ٱللَّهِ","d":"l-lahi","e":"(of) Allah","i":"اللّٰهِ"},{"b":"6.9","h":"10.9","c":"هُزُوٗا","d":"huzuwan","e":"(in) ridicule","i":"هُزُوًا"},{"b":"7.6","h":"12.15","c":"وَغَرَّتۡكُمُ","d":"wagharratkumu","e":"and deceived you","i":"وَّغَرَّتۡكُمُ"},{"b":"9.9","h":"15.47","c":"ٱلۡحَيَوٰةُ","d":"l-ḥayatu","e":"the life","i":"الۡحَيٰوةُ"},{"b":"10.9","h":"17.45","c":"ٱلدُّنۡيَاۚ","d":"l-dun'yā","e":"(of) the world","i":"الدُّنۡيَاۚ"},{"b":"12.8","h":"22.3","c":"فَٱلۡيَوۡمَ","d":"fal-yawma","e":"So this Day","i":"فَالۡيَوۡمَ"},{"b":"13.9","h":"23.96","c":"لَا","d":"lā","e":"not","i":"لَا"},{"b":"14.3","h":"24.73","c":"يُخۡرَجُونَ","d":"yukh'rajūna","e":"they will be brought forth","i":"يُخۡرَجُوۡنَ"},{"b":"15.6","h":"27","c":"مِنۡهَا","d":"min'hā","e":"from it","i":"مِنۡهَا"},{"b":"16.4","h":"28.5","c":"وَلَا","d":"walā","e":"and not","i":"وَلَا"},{"b":"17.0","h":"29.65","c":"هُمۡ","d":"hum","e":"they","i":"هُمۡ"},{"b":"17.4","h":"30.45","c":"يُسۡتَعۡتَبُونَ","d":"yus'taʿtabūna","e":"will be asked to appease","i":"يُسۡتَعۡتَبُوۡنَ"}],"a":{"g":"That is because you took the verses of Allah in ridicule, and worldly life deluded you.\" So that Day they will not be removed from it, nor will they be asked to appease [Allah]."}},"36":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.75","c":"فَلِلَّهِ","d":"falillahi","e":"Then for Allah","i":"فَلِلّٰهِ"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.71","c":"ٱلۡحَمۡدُ","d":"l-ḥamdu","e":"(is) all the praise","i":"الۡحَمۡدُ"},{"b":"2.0","h":"4.05","c":"رَبِّ","d":"rabbi","e":"(the) Lord","i":"رَبِّ"},{"b":"2.6","h":"5.13","c":"ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ","d":"l-samāwāti","e":"(of) the heavens","i":"السَّمٰوٰتِ"},{"b":"4.1","h":"7.99","c":"وَرَبِّ","d":"warabbi","e":"and (the) Lord","i":"وَرَبِّ"},{"b":"5.0","h":"9.53","c":"ٱلۡأَرۡضِ","d":"l-arḍi","e":"(of) the earth","i":"الۡاَرۡضِ"},{"b":"5.7","h":"10.81","c":"رَبِّ","d":"rabbi","e":"(the) lord","i":"رَبِّ"},{"b":"6.4","h":"12.07","c":"ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","d":"l-ʿālamīna","e":"(of) the worlds","i":"الۡعٰلَمِيۡنَ"}],"a":{"g":"Then, to Allah belongs [all] praise - Lord of the heavens and Lord of the earth, Lord of the worlds."}},"37":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.55","c":"وَلَهُ","d":"walahu","e":"And for Him","i":"وَلَهُ"},{"b":"0.63","h":"1.5","c":"ٱلۡكِبۡرِيَآءُ","d":"l-kib'riyāu","e":"(is) the greatness","i":"الۡكِبۡرِيَآءُ"},{"b":"3.8","h":"4.85","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"in","i":"فِى"},{"b":"4.1","h":"5.21","c":"ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ","d":"l-samāwāti","e":"the heavens","i":"السَّمٰوٰتِ"},{"b":"5.6","h":"8.02","c":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضِۖ","d":"wal-arḍi","e":"and the earth","i":"وَالۡاَرۡضِ​"},{"b":"6.7","h":"11.1","c":"وَهُوَ","d":"wahuwa","e":"and He","i":"وَهُوَ"},{"b":"7.3","h":"12.07","c":"ٱلۡعَزِيزُ","d":"l-ʿazīzu","e":"(is) the All-Mighty","i":"الۡعَزِيۡزُ"},{"b":"8.5","h":"14.14","c":"ٱلۡحَكِيمُ","d":"l-ḥakīmu","e":"the All-Wise","i":"الۡحَكِيۡمُ"}],"a":{"g":"And to Him belongs [all] grandeur within the heavens and the earth, and He is the Exalted in Might, the Wise."}}}